    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_URUGUAY_CASCOS_AZULES_STRATEGY">
      <Text>The Cascos Azules are a paratrooper replacement designed to be stationed abroad. They can be deployed in neutral lands to boost the production of new Cascos Azules units, or sent into conflict zones where they earn +10% combat strength for being outside friendly territory.</Text>
    </Row>
    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_HELP_URUGUAY_CASCOS_AZULES">
      <Text>Uruguayan unique paratrooper replacement. In addition to the normal abilities of a paratrooper, can enter foreign territory without open borders and gains +10% combat strength outside friendly territory. While more expensive than a normal paratrooper, gain +1% production (up to +40%) per unit within the borders of another civilization who you are not at war with.</Text>
    </Row>
